metadata.name: Andromedan #2
metadata.description: Just like earthlings are inspired by extraterrestrials, The Andromedan is inspired by earthlings. The Andromedans are settled in a galaxy that mirrors ours, but they transcend color, gender and class. Their chameleon skin tone fluctuates with moods, as they experience deep emotions on their galactic journeys. They are neither male or female, but beings of pure cosmic energy. The Andromedans live without labels, judgment, or social classes which allows them to eclipse stereotypes and live as expressions of true self love.  Vivid colors and unique style is the beacon for these space faring creators on their intergalactic travels.
